                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13212025" author="slebresne" created="Mon, 20 Feb 2012 18:50:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch is against 1.0. The patch:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;don&apos;t retry if we have enough columns to satisfy the initial query&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;keep the original count intact even if we do multiple retries.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;optimize the number of columns asked by a retry based on the ratio of number of column got/total asked on the initial query.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
